# Platform Info Inventories — When to Invoke

**Do not preload.** Invoke `/rebuild-platform-info-inventories` when you change platform gating artifacts.

## Triggers

| Change | Action |
|--------|--------|
| `*-access.ts` or page-access-registry | `Mode: refresh` · `Scope: surface=page` · `route=...` |
| `navigation.ts` or nav DB migration | `Mode: refresh` · `Scope: surface=navigation` |
| API permission guard | `Mode: refresh` · `Scope: surface=api` |
| Feature flag / plan limit enforcement | `Mode: refresh` · `surface=feature-flag` or `plan-limit` |
| New permission code (after migration) | `/create-update-rbac-permission` then refresh inventories |
| DRIFT_REPORT new items | `Mode: repair` |

## Commands

```bash
npm run rebuild:platform-info-inventories
npm run check:platform-info-inventories
```

## Skill

`.claude/skills/rebuild-platform-info-inventories/SKILL.md`

## Do not

- Hand-edit `docs/platform/inventories/GENERATED_*.md` or `platform-info-inventory.json`
- Use `/update-rbac-role` for seeding new permission codes (use `/create-update-rbac-permission`)
